Some gunmen have shot dead a mobile policeman in Warri, Delta State. It was gathered that the policeman was shot in the NPA New Port area on Friday. His AK47 rifle was reportedly taken away by his killers. A young man was also killed on Saturday in the Iyara axis of the oil city, The Nation learnt. Sources said his killing may be cult-related. Police spokesperson Onome Onovwakpoyeya confirmed the incidents.